      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so if i switch to a generator, it should stop the MemoryError, right? i'm worried though that there might be something else \"eating\" my memory in the background since the script stays high even when i'm not doing much. how can i tell if it's a legit leak or just how the objects are being handled?",
